description: Generate tests first; run the full suite; summarise coverage deltas.
globs:
  - "src/**/*"
alwaysApply: false
---

When editing or adding code under `src/`:

1. Write failing **unit + integration tests** for the desired behaviour.
2. Run the entire suite; confirm it fails for the right reason.
3. Implement code until all tests and linters pass.
4. Report coverage (% change) and note any uncovered edge‑cases.
